<p><a href="http://www.harqen.com/?utm_source=theResumator&amp;utm_medium=Web_Job_Boards&amp;utm_campaign=Test">HarQen</a> seeks a detail oriented, process-loving Client Services Manager to work in one of the most exciting start-up companies in the Milwaukee area. The CSM will manage the customer on-boarding and retention program for the company. Working with the sales team, the Client Services Manager is responsible for scheduling and conducting training sessions and fielding customer requests for assistance via telephone or email. This person would help clients get the most value from the product and maintain a high level of customer satisfaction.</p>
<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<p>•	Training new clients</p>
<p>•	Conducting client facing webinars</p>
<p>•	Answering questions about findings, methodology, and other related questions concerning the use of the software product</p>
<p>•	Performing a variety of activities to ensure customer satisfaction including interpreting findings, addressing product quality concerns and responding to general inquiries</p>
<p>•	Receiving requests for user assistance, identifies the source of the problem, determines appropriate course of action and coaches the user through the resolution process</p>
<p>•	Identifying potential up-sell opportunities of ancillary services and product sales through the course of conversing with customers and understanding their business needs</p>
<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<p>•	Bachelor’s degree</p>
<p>•	3-5 years experience as a Client Services Manager Sales representative for a software product or other technical product</p>
<p><strong>Salary/Benefits: </strong></p>
<p>Salary commensurate with experience: HarQen offers flexible benefits and compensation packages that allow our employees to make choices that fit their individual lifestyles.</p>
<p>Some of the benefits for full-time employees include the following: •	Health Insurance •	401K •	Minimum 15 days flexible time off, additional sick time, plus 10 paid holidays</p>
